  "text": [
    "I",
    "doubled corners",
    "of the situation",
    "the words duped by this dialectic",
    "know",
    "the pose of \u201cbrushing against\u201d",
    "insistence",
    "on detail",
    "severe eyelashes",
    "the weapons must",
    "be kept in order",
    "(take the",
    "game",
    "of courtesy",
    "of charm)",
    "her knees crossed",
    "over the manner of",
    "his undressing her",
    "a chord",
    "(deceptively resonant)",
    "a strength of image",
    "but scanty provisions interrupt",
    "her concerns for doors",
    "into sleep",
    "focuses",
    "the story can be carried in two hands",
    "finale:",
    "I have turned on",
    "with shifting strands",
    "of light"
  ],
  "title": "The Senses Barely or The Necessities of Life",
